        <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Link notebook: &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cua2FnZ2xlLmNvbS9jb2RlL2hhb3RpZW5kdWNhbmgvZG5uLWNubi1iZXJ0&#34;&gt;DNN-CNN-BERT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: I use tiny-bert model &lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/gaunernst/bert-tiny-uncased&#34;&gt; &lt;code&gt;gaunernst/bert-tiny-uncased&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/a&gt; to minimize computational resources&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;contents&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#contents&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Contents&lt;/h2&gt;
